headline: Moody’s (NYSE:MCO) Q3 Sales Beat Estimates
summary: Credit rating agency Moody's (NYSE:MCO) announced better-than-expected revenue in Q3 CY2025, with sales up 10.7% year on year to $2.01 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $3.92 per share was 6.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
